 mark the following dates : </p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<a href=\"http://www.t-dose.org/t-dose/node/122\">T-Dose 2009</a> will be held on 3 and 4 october in Eindhoven again.\n<p>Last year we had a nice Drupal track, some great MySQL talks and , a great unplanned Cloud talk , and different other interesting talks,  so this year promises also to be very interesting.<br />\n(PS.  Drupal Themers.. you might want to propose a new theme for the T-Dose site, who knows you\'ll even win something) </p>\n</li><li>For the first time , 2009 will be the year that Belgium will have it\'s own Security Conference,  <a href=\"http://brucon.be/\">BruCon</a> has just announced <a href=\"http://rationalsecurity.typepad.com/blog/\">Christofer Hoff</a> as a KeyNote speaker ,   BruCon will take place on 18 and 19 september... obviously in Brussels ;)\n</li><li>While we mention VirtSec I obviously should plug my own upcoming VirtSec talk at the <a href=\"http://www.lsec.be/index.php/whats_happening/event/secure_virtualization_seminar/\">LSec</a>  Secure Virtualization seminar on next Friday 13th\n</li></ul>\n<div class=\"technorati_tags\"><img alt=\"Technorati Tags:\" src=\"/blog/sites/all/modules/technorati/technobubble.gif\"/><strong>Technorati Tags: </strong><a href=\"http://technorati.com/tag/conferences\" rel=\"tag\">conferences</a> <a href=\"http://technorati.com/tag/drupal\" rel=\"tag\">drupal</a> <a href=\"http://technorati.com/tag/mysql\" rel=\"tag\">mysql</a> <a href=\"http://technorati.com/tag/open+source\" rel=\"tag\">open source</a> <a href=\"http://technorati.com/tag/security\" rel=\"tag\">security</a> <a href=\"http://technorati.com/tag/t-dose\" rel=\"tag\">t-dose</a> <a href=\"http://technorati.com/tag/virtsec\" rel=\"tag\">virtsec</a></div><div class=\"sharomaticbutton\"> <a href=\"http://www.shareomatic.com/http://www.krisbuytaert.be/blog/conference-time/shareomatic-drupal/Conference Time\"><img src=\"http://www.shareomatic.com/images/s_16_black.gif\" alt=\"Share with Shareomatic!\" \n			title=\"Post this item on various social news sites with Shareomatic!\"/></a> <a href=\"http://www.shareomatic.com/http://www.krisbuytaert.be/blog/conference-time/shareomatic-drupal/Conference Time\">Share with Shareomatic!</a> </div>\n<!--\n<rdf:RDF xmlns:rdf=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#\" xmlns:dc=\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\" xmlns:trackback=\"http://madskills.com/public/xml/rss/module/trackback/\">\n<rdf:Description rdf:about=\"http://www.krisbuytaert.be/blog/conference-time\" dc:identifier=\"http://www.krisbuytaert.be/blog/conference-time\" dc:title=\"Conference Time\" trackback:ping=\"http://www.krisbuytaert.be/blog/trackback/883\" />\n</rdf:RDF>\n-->\n<div id=\"trackback-url\"><div class=\"box\">\n\n  <h3>Trackback URL for this post:</h3>\n\n  <div class=\"content\">http://www.krisbuytaert.be/blog/trackback/883</div>\n</div>\n</div>',1235938972,'883 at http://www.krisbuytaert.be/blog'),(526,3,'CloudCamp Antwerp','http://www.krisbuytaert.be/blog/cloudcamp-antwerp-0','','<p>So yesterday a 100+ crowd met in the Antwerp Zoo.<br />\nI heard different comments from that crowd... some of them liked the event,  good networking, interresting topics , a broad overview, meeting new vendors active in the Cloud, others of them didn\'t .. it wasn\'t a real camp , just some vendors pitching,  they didn\'t hear any new stuff , or we didn\'t touch the real stuff.</p>\n<p>So different opinions from different expectations... </p>\n<p>Anyhow  for all those who could\'t read the slides :  </p>\n<div style=\"width:425px;text-align:left\" id=\"__ss_1271663\"><a style=\"font:14px Helvetica,Arial,Sans-serif;display:block;margin:12px 0 3px 0;text-decoration:underline;\" href=\"http://www.slideshare.net/KrisBuytaert/cloudsec-dont-forget-security-in-the-cloud?type=presentation\" title=\"CloudSec , don&#39;t forget Security in the Cloud !\">CloudSec , don&#39;t forget Security in the Cloud !</a>\n<object style=\"margin:0px\" width=\"425\" height=\"355\"><pa